  <div class="container">
    <img src="https://texascreditbenchmark.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/logo-6-e1751434403324.png" alt="Texas Credit Benchmark Logo">
    <h1>We'll Be Back Soon!</h1>
    <p>Our system is undergoing important updates for the next <strong>48 hours</strong> <strong class="ct">Central Time (CT).</strong> We appreciate your patience and will be back online shortly.</p>
    <div id="countdown">Loading countdown...</div>
    <p>Thank you for your patience.<br>â€” Texas Credit Benchmark Team</p>
